      "name": "Long COVID - Symptoms Due to COVID-19 - Screener",
      "code": "PX992001",
      "abbreviation": "PX992001",
      "description": "This screener measures new or continuing self-reported COVID-19 symptoms. There are 36 different symptoms included in the list along with the option of specifying additional not listed symptoms.",
